Oh Yeah!  Well, when you and all the Bros were in Vietnam. all Mom ever sent you was candy, cookies and presents ...'cause you're all sissies.<br>
But Mom didn't send me that kinda stuff...make me soft..no way..(God! the tears are rolling down my cheeks!)  Mom viewed me as her favorite..she sent me letter bombs..just to keep me alert... she honed that razor's edge, knowing that her Favorite Son would return...(I'm sobbing uncontrolably)<br>
I remember my welcome home...Mom changed her name (just before my DEROS) and moved out of town just to challenge my LRRP skills (what a Kidder!)..and the booby traps on the front porch (sniff!)..But, that's Mom for you...going out of her way to make me feel at home.<br><br>
Can't Write no more...(too choked up!)<br><br>
Mom's True Favorite - MTF
